## What Changed in Q3 FY26

Jain Resource Recycling Ltd (NSE: JAINREC) delivered a **strong volume-led quarter**.  
Top-line growth was sharp, but rising finance and employee costs kept margins under pressure.

This quarter is best understood as **scale first, efficiency later**.

